      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;1&#34;&gt;1&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;***Sri Vishnu Puraana, Amsha 4, Chapter 3, Shloka 1:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;2&#34;&gt;2&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Atah cha maandaatuh putra santatih abhidheeyate | ***&lt;em&gt;Maandhaatru&amp;rsquo;s putra santati&lt;/em&gt; is going to be told now. ***Sri Vishnu Puraana, Amsha 4, Chapter 3, Shloka 2: &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Ambareeshasya maandhaatru tanayasya yuvanaashvah putro abhoot&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;3&#34;&gt;3&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;| ***&lt;em&gt;Maandhaatru&amp;rsquo;s&lt;/em&gt; son &lt;em&gt;Ambareesha&lt;/em&gt; had a son by name &lt;em&gt;Yuvanaashva&lt;/em&gt;. ***Sri Vishnu Puraana, Amsha 4, Chapter 3, Shloka 3: &lt;br&gt;&#xA;Tasmaat haareetah yato angiraso haaritaah | ***&lt;em&gt;Youvanaashva&lt;/em&gt; had a son &lt;em&gt;Haareeta&lt;/em&gt;, and because of &lt;em&gt;Haareeta&lt;/em&gt;, the &lt;em&gt;Angirasaas&lt;/em&gt;. ***Sri Engal Aalwaan&amp;rsquo;s Commentary:&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Tasmaat iti | Yato angirasa iti | Atha haaritaanaam tryaarsyeyaah&lt;/p&gt;</description>
